#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/hardware_network/epos_ssc.rst:63
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Network Security --> SSL/TLS --> Certificate`."
msgstr "עבור אל :menuselection:`Network Security --> SSL/TLS --> Certificate`."

