msgstr "עבור ל:menuselection:`מלאי --> הגדרות --> הגדרות`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/hardware_network/scale.rst:51
msgid ""
"Scroll down to the :guilabel:`Products` section and "
