msgid ""
"Configure the cash machine itself before setting it up in Odoo. Currently, "
"Odoo supports :doc:`Glory <cash_machines/glory>` "
"and :doc:`Cashdro<cash_machines/cashdro>` cash machines. Once the cash "
"machine is fully set up:"
msgstr ""
