msgstr ""
":ref:`התקן <general/install>` את המודול :guilabel:`POS Cashdro Cash "
"Machines`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashdro.rst:56
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/dpo.rst:48
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/tyro.rst:39
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Configuration --> Payment Methods` "
"and click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"עבור אל :menuselection:`קופה --> תצורה --> אמצעי תשלום` ולחץ על "
":guilabel:`חדש`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashdro.rst:58
msgid "Set the :guilabel:`Journal` field to :guilabel:`Cash`."
msgstr "הגדר את השדה :guilabel:`יומן` ל:guilabel:`מזומן`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashdro.rst:59
msgid "Select the relevant POS in the :guilabel:`Point of Sale` field."
msgstr "בחר את הקופה הרלוונטית בשדה :guilabel:`קופה`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashdro.rst:60
msgid ""
"Set the :guilabel:`Integration` field to :guilabel:`Cash Machine (Cashdro)`."
msgstr ""
"הגדר את השדה :guilabel:`אינטגרציה` ל:guilabel:`Cash Machine (Cashdro)`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashdro.rst:61
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Cashdro Settings` tab, enter the Cashdro machine's IP "
"address in the :guilabel:`Cashdro IP` field."
msgstr ""
"בכרטיסייה :guilabel:`הגדרות Cashdro`, הזן את כתובת ה-IP של מכונת Cashdro "
"בשדה :guilabel:`Cashdro IP`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashdro.rst:63
msgid ""
"Enter your Cashdro user credentials in the :guilabel:`Cashdro Username` "
"and :guilabel:`Cashdro Password` fields."
msgstr ""
"הזן את אישורי המשתמש שלך ב-Cashdro בשדות :guilabel:`שם משתמש Cashdro` ו-"
":guilabel:`סיסמת Cashdro`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashdro.rst:65
msgid "Enable :guilabel:`Cashdro Local Network Access`."
msgstr "הפעל :guilabel:`גישת רשת מקומית ל-Cashdro`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashdro.rst:68
msgid ""
"It is highly recommended to use :doc:`Local Network Access <../../"
"hardware_network/pos_lna>`, as it bypasses the need for an :doc:`SSL "
"certificate <../../hardware_network/epos_ssc>`."
msgstr ""
"מומלץ מאוד להשתמש ב-:doc:`גישת רשת מקומית <../../hardware_network/pos_lna>`, "
"מכיוון שהיא עוקפת את הצורך ב-:doc:`אישור SSL <../../hardware_network/"
"epos_ssc>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashdro.rst:72
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:134
